title: Ebro In The Morning - Super Bowl LVI Hip-Hop Halftime Show Recap
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 2/14/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the hip-hop halftime show at the Super Bowl (31), and Valentine's Day (1).

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
